# Cloudflare Settings for omaxeeternity2.in
# Stack: GitHub Pages + Cloudflare DNS/CDN + Hostinger Domain

## 1. Caching (Cloudflare → Caching → Configuration)
- Caching Level: Standard
- Browser Cache TTL: 4 hours
- Always Online: ON

## 2. Speed Optimizations (Cloudflare → Speed → Optimization)
- Auto Minify JS: ON
- Auto Minify CSS: ON
- Auto Minify HTML: ON
- Rocket Loader: ON

## 3. Security Headers (Cloudflare → Rules → Transform Rules → Modify Response Header)
Add these as HTTP Response Headers:
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin

## 4. SSL/TLS (Cloudflare → SSL/TLS)
- SSL Mode: Full (Strict)
- Always Use HTTPS: ON
- HTTP Strict Transport Security (HSTS): ON

## 5. Firewall (Optional – Cloudflare → Security → WAF)
- Security Level: Medium
- Bot Fight Mode: ON
